à l'établissement hors site

245
00:13:50,789 --> 00:13:52,332
afin que vous puissiez
vérifier le tout.

246
00:13:52,415 --> 00:13:53,416
CORRESPONDANCE FACIALE
WILL SAWYER

247
00:13:55,377 --> 00:13:56,419
Merci.

248
00:13:56,503 --> 00:13:57,921
